race.comment: FORNER'S REIGN (1) clocked a scintillating 21.56 win over 380m at this track last start. Has the ability and looks a key chance again. ROYAL BLOOD (2) has shown good improvement at his last two starts, hitting the frame latest when 2nd at this track over 380m. Leading chance. RUMBLE TEMPEST (4) was strongly fancied latest and proved too good with a 1.5 lengths win at this track in a handy 21.77. Awkwardly drawn but has a good record over this journey. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Can make it two on the bounce. SHE'S SNAPPY (5) is in the mix after placing as favourite last time out.
